name: SUTOHONO Justice II
description:
Fap Sutohono was the concept manager and deep code creator of the first law procedures powered by artificial intelligence. 5 editions. As a man of justice Sutohono cannot participate in battles but he can be a referee if he is asked for. He will receive a bonus for this service at the end of the battle. This bonus is not fixed and depends on the average power of both players. Full list of Properties will be announced soon.
